Third Department,

April, 1968 *

(April 16, 1968) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Ralph Scott, Petitioner, v. Edwin La Vallee, as Warden of Clinton Prison, Respondent.

Not published with other decisions of April 16, 1968, 29 A D 2d 993. [Rep.

Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (subd. [b], par. 2) for a writ of habeas corpus denied, for failure of compliance with article 70 of the CPLR, and more particularly with the provisions of CPLR 7002 (subd. [c], pars. 5, 6) thereof, and as otherwise insufficient on its face. Gibson, P. J., Herlihy, Reynolds, Staley, Jr., and Gabrielli, JJ., concur.
